assert Function.expand_variadic(arguments, amount) == expected
pytest.mark.parametrize('arguments, amount, expected', [([Bool, Integer,
    ...], 5, [Bool, Integer, Integer, Integer, Integer]), ([Bool, Integer,
    ...], 2, [Bool, Integer]), ([Bool, Integer, ...], 1, None), ([Real, ...
    ], 2, [Real, Real]), ([Real], 1, [Real]), ([Real, Real], 1, None), ([
    Real, Real], 3, None)])
